    "After the above screening, 140 articles remained for full-text assessment, and we applied the exclusion criteria again and obtained 99 published articles.",
    "Our search on SSRN initially returned 30 articles.",
    "We removed 24 articles based on our exclusion criteria, leaving six unpublished articles.",
    "Subsequently, we conducted backward snowballing on 105 articles included in the keyword searches (i.e., we went through the references of the included articles) to find additional articles that did not appear in the keyword searches.",
